Member, Board of Directors

                    2013 - Current                  


Tecnoglass, Inc.

                    Tecnoglass, Inc. operates as a holding company, which engages in the design, manufacture, and trade of architectural glass. Its products include the following types of glass: laminated, thermo-laminated, tempered, silk-screened, curved, and digital print. It also distributes floating facades, bathroom dividers, automatic doors, and hurricane-proof and commercial display windows. The company operates under the Alutions by TG and Alutions trademarks. Tecnoglass was founded on September 21, 2011 and is headquartered in Barranquilla, Colombia.                  




Director

                    1997 - Current                  


C.I. Energia Solar SA

                    C.I. Energia Solar SA manufactures industrial glass, windows and associated aluminum products. Its products include windows, doors, storefronts, window wall systems and curtain wall systems. The company was founded by Jose Manuel Daes and Christian T. Daes on March 11, 1984 and is headquartered in Barranquilla, Colombia.                  




Director

                    1995 - Current                  


Tecnoglass SA

                    Part of Energy Holding Corp., Tecnoglass SA is a Colombian company located in Barranquilla that manufactures industrial glass, windows and associated aluminum products. It was founded by José Manuel Daes. On 20 Dec 13 Tecnoglass, Inc. acquired Tecnoglass SA .                  





